      <title>尼日利亚与国际金融公司签署奈拉融资协议以降低货币风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/nigeria-signs-naira-funding-deal-with-ifc-to-cut-currency-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚央行与国际金融公司签署了一项促进本币融资的协议，希望刺激对奈拉的需求，同时帮助企业避免外币借款的汇率风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/nigeria-signs-naira-funding-deal-with-ifc-to-cut-currency-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 12:32:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多竞争对手承诺取消许多新建住宅的联邦销售税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/trudeau-rival-pledges-to-axe-federal-sales-tax-on-many-new-homes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保守党领袖皮埃尔·波利耶夫 (Pierre Poilievre) 表示，如果他当选总理，他将取消加拿大针对售价低于 100 万加元（719,700 美元）的新房征收的 5% 的全国销售税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/trudeau-rival-pledges-to-axe-federal-sales-tax-on-many-new-homes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 12:18:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡车制造商 Scania 计划全面转向 Northvolt，以推动电池业务转型</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/scania-plans-complete-shift-to-northvolt-in-lift-to-battery-firm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大众汽车集团旗下的卡车制造品牌斯堪尼亚计划为其未来的所有电动卡车配备 Northvolt 电池，此举对这家资金短缺的瑞典电池制造商表示信任，目前该公司正努力达成救助方案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/scania-plans-complete-shift-to-northvolt-in-lift-to-battery-firm</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 12:04:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>调查显示，无论哈里斯还是特朗普执政，美国财富都将增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/harris-or-trump-stocks-are-ready-to-roar-either-way-survey-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[预计在两位候选人的领导下，股市都会上涨。特朗普对黄金和比特币的利好预期有所改善，而哈里斯对住房成本的利好预期略有改善。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/harris-or-trump-stocks-are-ready-to-roar-either-way-survey-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 12:00:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
